items.title: Worth the wait: Giants keep Dodgers reeling
items.summary: The Dodgers' historic spiral continued Monday night and well into Tuesday morning. In a game delayed twice by weather for a total of more than 3 1/2 hours, the last-place Giants' 8-6 win at AT&T Park extended the Dodgers' losing streak to a Los Angeles record 11 with their 16th defeat in 17 games.
